Looking back to these past 4 years is surreal. Didn't know what to expect at all during the start of this journey. Doubting myself constantly in the early days because of the university's reputation of being the best. But that all changed, gradually. I learned that what makes this institution great is not only the quality of the academic studies, but rather on the contagious spirit of excellence it constantly emits to it's inhabitants. I can honestly say that I've achieved more than what I could've imagined at the start. Now, I'm grateful for the opportunity this institution has given to me and I will never forget what I think are the most important moments in my life thus far. So for one last time. 
Untuk Tuhan, Bangsa, dan Almamater. 
Jonathan Putera

I believe Studentscatalyst is a place for me to grow together with the best college students from different backgrounds.
